  "body": "Run Proposer boost in testnet for 2-3 days to test for stability.\r\n- [x] [kintsugi](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3678#issuecomment-1025100934)\r\n  - [x] start node with proposer boost \r\n  - [x] Observe proposer boost not being applied while syncing\r\n  - [x] Observe proposer boost being applied on timely block and it being the next head (typically)\r\n  - [x] Observer proposer boost not being applied on skipped slot\r\n  - [x] Stable run for 2~3 days\r\n  - [x] metrics :\r\n    - Nothing out of the usual but a sudden drop in peercount midway, most probably because of local internet conditions\r\n- [x] [prater](https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3678#issuecomment-1025101862)\r\n  - [x] start node with proposer boost\r\n  - [x] Observe proposer boost not being applied while syncing\r\n  - [x]  Observe proposer boost being applied on timely block and it being the next head (typically)\r\n  - [x] Observe proposer boost not being applied on skipped slot\r\n  - [x] Stable run for 2-3 days\r\n  - [x] metrics :\r\n    - Nothing out of the usual but a sudden drop in peercount midway, most probably because of local internet conditions\r\n\r\nContext: https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/3506#issuecomment-1023888079",
